<title>FRANCE: Havas Advertising H1 net up 16 percent.</title>
<headline>Havas Advertising H1 net up 16 percent.</headline>
<dateline>PARIS 1996-10-03</dateline>
<text>
<p>Six months to Sept 30, 1996.</p>
<p>(Figures in millions of French francs unless stated)</p>
<p>    Net attributable after exceptional    93.4  vs   80.5</p>
<p>    Operating				    219.5  vs  211.8</p>
<p>    Pre-tax, pre-exceptional		  93.3  vs   81.1</p>
<p>    Exceptional losses			  32.1  vs   19.4</p>
<p>    Financial  charges			  28.5  vs   27.1</p>
<p>    Turnover				  13,377    vs 12,792</p>
<p>NOTE - Havas Advertising said that for the full year 1996 it should see, both for its operating margin and its results, the biggest rise since 1992.</p>
<p>-- Paris Newsroom +33 1 4221 5452</p>
